How is the procedure for applying a permanent in the salon Ukrainian Beauty

A full session of permanent makeup takes 2 to 3 hours and includes several important steps:

  1- After signing up for a consultation and a personal meeting with the master, you get a competent individual consultation, where all points, the presence of contraindications, individual reactions of the body, wishes and recommendations on the shape, color and variety of permanent makeup are discussed in detail. After that, an allergy patch test is done and only 48 hours after that, if you do not have a reaction, we carry out the procedure.

  2- Proper preparation for the procedure is one of the main components of a good result. It includes the selection of the form, technique of applying the permanent, materials and preparations.

  3- Complete mutual understanding and trust is important to us, which is why the master additionally coordinates with you every stroke of the future transformation, drawing up a detailed sketch, taking into account the color type and shape of the face.

  4- The next steps are applying the permanent. Upon completion of the procedure, you receive advice on care and proper recovery.

  5- To consolidate the perfect result, some time after healing, the master conducts a control examination, if necessary, correcting the halftones and tightening the color.

  6- Enjoyment in a perfect way and complete freedom from cosmetics.
